name: NYDailyNews
text:
The Mets hope to open the short season in Queens on July 24 with a series against the Braves, health-permitting.

Four Braves recover from the coronavirusm including Freddie Freeman who had “body aches, headaches, chills and a high fever.”

text:
Friends and family of Jose Cepada — the first of 9 to die in a wave of Fourth of July weekend violence — took to social media to mourn, and condem the gun violence that took his life.

Cepada, 20, was shot to death in East New York.
